Week 1: Project Initiation & Research

Objectives:

Understanding the project requirements and scope.

Conducting research on expert matching systems and existing solutions.

Identifying key features and technologies to be used in the project.



Tasks Completed:

Defined the problem statement and project goals.

Researched different expert matching algorithms and methodologies.

Identified the required technologies: React.js, Node.js, MongoDB, Python (for ML), Express.js.

Prepared a preliminary project roadmap with milestones.



Challenges Faced:

Difficulty in deciding the best approach for expert matching.

Evaluating different databases (MongoDB vs. PostgreSQL) for optimal performance.



Next Steps:

Design wireframes and database schema.

Start working on the frontend and backend setup.